{"tid":220320,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"主人玩水又玩屎","createTime":"2017-04-28T00:55:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T00:56:43.000Z","uid":110966,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"912b7e4eca69a7a99d6ed246d0692fe0294e55dd","tid":220320,"uid":110966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T00:56:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: medium;\">已經玩左幾個禮拜，佢係咁伸隻手入去撥水搞到我水兜冇晒水或者好多貓砂係底，一換即玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">玩屎嗰下先死，好學唔學學人玩屎！！？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">啲屎條屙係貓砂道溝埋，就好似樂嘉杏仁糖差張金紙係出面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢當啲杏仁屎係波咁，係咁撥搞到周地屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求教點先可以令主人佢唔玩水玩屎，佢而家半歲大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1682a9a4420ffd466ad10848df9b92d6736768","tid":220320,"uid":863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T00:56:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}